{"tid":1147884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無男朋友係咁樣？","createTime":"2019-05-10T06:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T08:57:58.000Z","uid":192423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9efaabd2c65e5ab536a83057ce7c9c81fbb30954","tid":1147884,"uid":192423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"平時都知佢唔鐘意多人<br />\n諗住今個星期去睇復仇者<br />\n應該過佐一輪無咁多人<br />\n點知佢話要唔多人同無人嘈既場<br />\n仲話要有情侶座既院先睇<br />\n我o哂咀，咁有要求？<br />\n之前睇戲都無咁麻煩<br />\n其實睇場戲姐<br />\n之後約親佢打波都係甩底<br />\n我朝咁早起身book場，哂佐我心機<br />\n每次都煮飯俾佢食<br />\n又就哂佢，對我都咁差？<br />\n好灰心<br />\n有諗過大家其實唔夾"},{"pid":"a1129a39fbf5c5db02aa2248e3b6c828239e225a","tid":1147884,"uid":171615,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"如果佢同你夾嘅你就唔會中意佢啦"},{"pid":"6eeef3c2ce3e22902a01aabd2b325ce5448c6eb1","tid":1147884,"uid":181283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1129a39fbf5c5db02aa2248e3b6c828239e225a","tid":1147884,"uid":171615,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"如果佢同你夾嘅你就唔會中意佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"岩聽"},{"pid":"148e36dc71568d2184ad6877acfc4616e81c7b28","tid":1147884,"uid":192423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a1129a39fbf5c5db02aa2248e3b6c828239e225a","tid":1147884,"uid":171615,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"如果佢同你夾嘅你就唔會中意佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"係覺得大家相處開始辛苦"},{"pid":"b5050dfdc96595cd0de45de07d3894b7eaecb435","tid":1147884,"uid":230620,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"兩個男人去公眾地方又係尷尬啲嘅"},{"pid":"0c4ff661f899959e6d1de3b115a2b25d09f9e97b","tid":1147884,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"扑野算啦<br />\n都係鴨姐"},{"pid":"13afefbee5288ed685c2579ad5885685217f63e3","tid":1147884,"uid":192423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s